                icon: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="22"></line><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line></svg>`,
